<plot>"Marcano... El Show" was the talk show that had the highest ratings of Puerto Rican television during 1990 when it first aired. It kept strong ratings during 1992 when it was released on Telemundo Network in the United States during the midnight slot. The show had interviews, musical guests, and comedy.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?357355</url></doc>
